00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.360
Today we're going to talk about <b>five</b> of

00:00:01.360 --> 00:00:03.040
the most popular ways to mix <b>cocktails</b>.

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:06.001
Shaking, double shaking, stirring,

00:00:06.321 --> 00:00:08.281
building, and blending. In this episode,

00:00:08.281 --> 00:00:09.561
I'm going to try and help you understand

00:00:09.561 --> 00:00:10.841
which technique you use when you're

00:00:10.841 --> 00:00:12.841
making certain drinks, the impact it has

00:00:12.841 --> 00:00:14.282
on the drink, and also give you some

00:00:14.282 --> 00:00:15.762
examples of drinks that use each

00:00:15.762 --> 00:00:18.082
technique. So let's have a look at it.